variable nrrtemp
;
;
; Greater Elemental
MNUMBER 132
ADJECTIVE 4
NAME elemental
;Description dude!!!
;  Make sure you include the fact they have 
;  claws to cut through rock with!!!
*DESCRIPTION_START
The creature before you resembles a normal fire elemental only in shape, it 
looms above you and has claws of flame that look as if that could melt  
steel.
*DESCRIPTION_END
HUMAN
RACE 21
ETERNAL
DISCORPORATE
ATTACK1 500
BODY 750
EXTRABODY 500
DEFENSE 175
ARMOR 50
SPEED 2
STRATEGY 501
WEAPON 1703 -1 10
MAGICWEAPON 21
SPELL 118
SPELLSKILL 300
SPELLUSE 20
MANA 500
; entangle
IMMUNITY 0 0
; crushing
IMMUNITY 1 2
; edged weapons
IMMUNITY 2 2
; heat 0x dmg
IMMUNITY 3 0
; electricity
IMMUNITY 4 0
; cold 2x dmg
IMMUNITY 5 4
; charm,sleep
IMMUNITY 6 0
; life affecting
IMMUNITY 7 0
; death crits
IMMUNITY 9 0
;
; Text stuff goes here!
;
TEXI The blow passes through the body of the elemental without any effect.
TEXD disapears in a gout of flame.
TEXM A greater elemental drifts
TEXE A greater elemental rises from the lava pool.
TEXS A greater elemental seems to grow slightly.
TEXL A greater elemental throws a flaming ball of fire.
TEXQ The tremor shrinks back to its normal size.
;
;
NUMBER 2300
NAME Underground, Lakeshore
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS	
CHANNEL 134
REGION 131
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are standing on the eastern shore of an underground lake. Wisps of steam 
float up from the surface of the lake filling the air with sulferous fumes.
The lakeshore is made of shiny black sand which scatters any light.
A low rumbing sound echos from the walls of this chamber.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 2301
; item 0 water
ITEM 0 1062
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The water rolls and bubbles as steam rises from its surface.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You start to enter the water but pull back from the heat.
  ECHO OTHERS Yo see %N aproach the water and then pull back.
ENDIF
;
;
NUMBER 2301
NAME Underground, Lava Tunnel
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS
CHANNEL 134
REGION 131
*DESCRIPTION_START
This tunnel is roughly round in shape and the walls are very smooth as if they 
were melted. The air in here is very hot and full of fumes making it difficult 
to breath. A low rumbling sound can be heard in the distance.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 2300
EXIT N 2303
EXIT E 2302
