NUMBER 2304
NAME Underground, Lava Tunnel
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS
CHANNEL 134
REGION 131
*DESCRIPTION_START
This tunnel is roughly round in shape and the walls are very smooth as if they 
were melted. A crack in the floor allows foul vapors to fill the room. The air
in here is very hot and the fumes make it difficult to breath. Heat flows in 
waves from the east. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 2303
EXIT E 2309
; add fumes damage... see lab in tower
RANDOM nrrtemp 1 100 0
IFVAR nrrtemp > 80
  ECHO PLAYER You begin coughing as you inhale some of the fumes.
  ECHO OTHERS %N coughs from the fumes.
  DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 8 The fumes in the air burn as you inhale them.
ENDIF
