NUMBER 2307
NAME Underground, Lair
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS
CHANNEL 134
REGION 131
*DESCRIPTION_START
This cave seems to have been created by a pocket of gas trapped in the lava 
durring the forming of the volcano. Fish bones and debris are scattered about 
the cave as if something lives here. A loud roaring sound comes from a opening 
in the wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT SE 2305
;item 0 opening
ITEM 0 72 VAL2=2308
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You see an opening to the south where part of the wall seems to have collapsed.
ENDIF
IFNOITEM 9
  IFENTRY
    NEWITEM 9 693
    GENMON 285
    GENMON 285
    GENMON 285
    GENMON 285
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFNOITEM 8
  IFITEM 9
    IFENTRY
      NEWITEM 8 693
    GENMON 285
    GENMON 285
    GENMON 285
    GENMON 285
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
