NUMBER 2315
NAME Underground, Natural Cavern
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS
CHANNEL 134
REGION 131
*DESCRIPTION_START
This cavern appears to be a natural formation. Large piles of stone are 
scattered about the room where they appear to have fallen from the ceiling.
There is an opening in the wall to the west.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 63 VAL2=2314
ITEM 1 72 VAL2=2316
IFSAY ZZZZZZZZZZZ
  echo player don't fall asleep now.
ELSE
  RANDOM nrrtemp 1 100 0
  IFVAR nrrtemp > 50
    ECHO PLAYER You voice echos off the ceiling causing part of it to fall on you.
    DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 10  You take damage from the falling rock.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
