NUMBER 2316
NAME Underground, Lavalake
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS	
CHANNEL 134
REGION 131
*DESCRIPTION_START
You find youself in a large chamber with a pool of lava in the center. The 
walls look melted and strange furrows can be seen in their surfaces. An opening
leads out.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 1 72 VAL2=2315
ITEM 2 1575 UNLOCKED
; item 0 pool
ITEM 0 736
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR MONINROOM = 0
    ECHO PLAYER You notice a chest within the pool of lava.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You can't see into the pool past the creatures.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You try to enter the lava pool but pull back from the heat.
  ECHO OTHERS Yo see %N aproach the lava pool and then pull back.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB OPEN 2
  ECHO PLAYER You grasp the lid of the chest.
  DAMAGEPLR BURN 100 You burn your hands on the lid.
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 2
  ECHO PLAYER You burn yourself as you come in contact with the chest.
  DAMAGEPLR BURN 100 Blisters appear where you touched the chest.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
  ECHO PLAYER You attempt to enter the pool of lava, but are forced back but the intense heat.
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 0
  ECHO PLAYER You reach out to touch the lava, but are driven back by the heat.
ENDIF
